  "title": "Corporate Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>Our company is a market leader in the wholesale supply of general & industrial hardware and accessories, we are expanding our team and we welcome you to apply with us as a Corporate Sales Executive.<br /><br />Location : West Area<br /><br /><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Drive Sales / Business Development activities to acquire new corporate clients through cold callingAchieve and meet sales targets on a monthly basis</li><li>Ensure optimal level of customers’ satisfaction is met at all time</li><li>Build / Nurture relationship with new customers</li><li>To build a pipeline through outbound activities and develop new qualified opportunities.</li><li>To provide timely sales support to customer, upselling and providing alternative solutions when appropriate.</li><li>Review sales enquiries and prepare sales quotation for submission.</li><li>Follow up on sales enquiries, gather feedback on sales quotation and market information.</li><li>To work with account department to ensure prompt and accurate payment collection from customers.</li><li>To work with operation team to ensure on time delivery to customers.</li><li>To build rapport and maintain relationships with both existing and new customers.</li><li>Undertake any other tasks as assigned</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Strong written and verbal communication skills to liaise with English & Mandarin speaking clients</li><li>Good time management skills</li><li>Strong interpersonal and teamwork skills</li><li>Strong desire to learn along with professional drive</li><li>Minimum diploma in any discipline</li><li>Good interpersonal, communication and co-ordination skills</li><li>Have a strong sense of urgency & responsibility, meticulous & good follow up skill</li><li>Excellent knowledge of Microsoft Office</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
